  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You extend your Chakra creating a 30-foot radius bubble of Chakra, that occasionally crackles with a soft yellow Lightning. For the duration of this jutsu, the aura moves with you, centered on you. If used in combat, the duration of this jutsu becomes \"Concentration, 1 minute\" and each creature of your choice, that begins its turn within your aura has its speed increased by 15 feet until the end of their next turn. If used during exploration or land travel, its duration becomes 1 hour and you treat normal travel pace as Fast travel pace.</p>",
